description:
"Submersible Setback" John Behring Dan Dworkin, Jay Beattie November 14, 2005 

Jackson helps Laura and Rich build a submersible so that they can visit a site where the creatures spawn. Meanwhile, the Bennetts consider boot camp as a way to discipline Miles. Ultimately Miles ends up working at the aquriam instead as his sister is sympathetic to his plight and convinces her parents not to punish him as he trully cared about Nimrod.
